<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">That each United States Attorney shall establish or participate in a task force on human trafficking.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb4dd5c66-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/119/74/dA/tII">Pub. L. 119–74, div. A, title II</ref>, <date date="2026-01-23">Jan. 23, 2026</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/140/19">140 Stat. 19</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
